OL,3,CFormer priest faced with sex abuse
OL,4,Ccharges carried out 'exorcisms'
OL,6,FJersey's Royal Court heard how a
OL,7,Fformer Catholic Priest, charged with
OL,8,Ften counts of sexual abuse against a
OL,9,Fchild, carried out 'exorcisms' on his
OL,10,Falleged victim.
OL,12,FPiotr Antoni Glas, 61, faces eight
OL,13,Fcharges of gross indecency and two
OL,14,Fcounts of indecent assault for alleged
OL,15,Fincidents involving a boy aged between
OL,16,F13 and 15.
OL,18,FWitnesses took the stand today
OL,19,F(Thursday, 3 April) to give evidence
OL,20,Ffor the prosecution of Mr Glas.
