OL,3,CFormer priest faced with sex abuse
OL,4,Ccharges carried out 'exorcisms'
OL,6,FThe court was told how Mr Glas would
OL,7,F'playfight' with the complainant
OL,8,Fbefore committing sexually motivated
OL,9,Facts between 2004 and 2007.
OL,11,FThe court heard how the alleged victim
OL,12,Fwould occasionally sit on his lap and
OL,13,F"play wrestling games" with him.
OL,15,FA witness said she saw Glas with a
OL,16,Fblack eye after the teenager had
OL,17,Fallegedly attacked him to free himself
OL,18,Fafter his face had been held against
OL,19,Fthe priest's groin.
