OL,3,CFormer priest faced with sex abuse
OL,4,Ccharges carried out 'exorcisms'
OL,6,FAs a result, the priest carried out a
OL,7,Fseries of exorcisms on the victim, as
OL,8,FGlas said he felt the victim was
OL,9,F"possessed".
OL,11,FThe witness said that during the
OL,12,Fspiritual practices designed to expel
OL,13,F'the devil', the boy got "very angry
OL,14,Fand tried to get the defendant off
OL,15,Fhim."
OL,17,FShe added that during these exorcisms,
OL,18,Fthe victim would be held down by two
OL,19,Fmen, with Glas talking to him in
OL,20,FLatin, breathing over him and putting
OL,21,Foil on him.
