OL,3,CFormer priest faced with sex abuse
OL,4,Ccharges carried out 'exorcisms'
OL,6,FThe witness said: "I wish I had the
OL,7,Fcourage to say stop." She added that
OL,8,Fshe felt "horrified" they had let it
OL,9,Fhappen.
OL,11,FAs the witness was questioned, Glas
OL,12,Fwould often have his eyes closed in
OL,13,Fthe dock, sometimes looking up to the
OL,14,Fceiling and rocking back and forth,
OL,15,Fholding prayer beads in his right hand.
OL,17,FEarlier in the trial, the court heard
OL,18,Fhow the defendant had a sexual
OL,19,Finterest involving feet - a 'foot
OL,20,Ffetish' that police say goes back many
OL,21,Fyears.
